name: Cellophane
description: Cellophane is a symbol of fear. Behind it you can hide your kits. Through cellophane, the world looks blurry and fuzzy. Sometimes people can only see the best in yourself under cellophane, and the downside is blurred. But is that a good thing? The only way to become a person is to combine pros and cons, when you realize that the real world is not so smooth and beautiful, and most of all, you’re not afraid to show yourself.
